Tags: virt, talk

I participated in the [virtualization panel](http://oclug.on.ca/meeting/48/) for my local [Linux Users Group](http://oclug.on.ca/) last night.  Pictures
from last night are up on [Richard Guy Briggs'](http://tricolour.net/photos/2009/10/01/oclug.html) website.

I've put up the slides for the [virtualization primer](http://www.jukie.net/~bart/slides/virt-intro/) talk, and also the [source document](http://git.jukie.net/virt-intro.git)
(created in [Inkscape](http://www.inkscape.org/)) for rendering the slides.  You will need [negative](http://github.com/bartman/negative) to do the latter.
